Detailed Description

cvmx_pnb::_pprsp_ff_sbe_info

This register contains information on single-bit ECC errors that occured in the response FIFO for cnMIPS requests to SMEM. These correspond to PNB(0..1)_INT_SUM[MEM12_SBE] interrupts.
